This directory contains regression tests for open issues that demonstrate bugs
which still exist in the current ledger build. These tests are written against
the CURRENT (incorrect) behavior so they pass, but they document the expected
behavior in comments.

Once a bug is fixed, the corresponding test should be updated to reflect the
correct behavior and moved to test/regress/.

These tests are NOT run by default in the test suite (ctest). They serve as a
tracking mechanism for known issues.
